
The system is backed by a MySQL database containing four tables:
CashierInfo:
Stores cashier credentials. CashierID (varchar) primary key and CashierName (varchar)

CustomerInfo:
Tracks customer details. CustomerNumber (int) primary key, CustomerName (varchar), Rewards (int)

Inventory:
Manages the stock, item names, and unique IDs for products. ItemID (varchar) primary key, ItemName (varchar), Stock (int)

Discount:
Holds price and discount details for each product. ItemID (varchar) foreign key, Price (decimal), Discount (decimal)

